# Styling and UI Guidelines

## Design System

This project uses DaisyUI with Tailwind CSS for consistent styling.

### Color Scheme

- Primary: Purple gradient (`from-purple-700 to-purple-400`)
- Base: Light theme (`data-theme="light"`)
- Background: `bg-base-200` for main background
- Cards: `bg-base-100` with `shadow-xl`

### Component Guidelines

#### Search Component

- Use `input input-bordered input-lg` for search input
- Include search icon with proper positioning
- Show/hide clear button based on input state
- Display results count with `text-base-content/70`

#### Card Layout

- Use `card card-compact` for consistent sizing
- Apply `hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300` for interactions
- Use `border-t-4 border-primary` for accent
- Maintain responsive grid: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`

#### Typography

- Headers: Use gradient text with `bg-clip-text text-transparent`
- Body text: Use `text-base-content/70` for secondary text
- Badges: Use `badge badge-primary` for highlights

### Responsive Design

- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`
- Flexible grid system
- Proper spacing with `px-4 sm:px-8`

### Accessibility

- Use semantic HTML elements
- Include proper `alt` attributes for images
- Ensure sufficient color contrast
- Use descriptive button text and titles
- Implement proper focus management

### Search UI Components

- Search input: `input input-bordered input-lg w-full pr-12 pl-12`
- Search icon: Positioned with `absolute left-4 top-1/2`
- Clear button: `btn btn-ghost btn-sm` with conditional visibility
- Results display: `text-center text-sm text-base-content/70`

### Card Components

- Container: `girl-card card card-compact bg-base-100 shadow-xl`
- Hover effects: `hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300`
- Border accent: `border-t-4 border-primary`
- Image container: `h-64` with `object-cover`
- Badge styling: `badge badge-secondary badge-outline gap-2`
